# Article Demo — Prompt Injection Detection
# Focused GIF showing violation detection + evidence packaging
# Run: cd demo && vhs article-demo.tape

Output "article-demo.gif"

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 920
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set CursorBlink false

Type "bash article-demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Sleep 3s
